OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,FThe Health Minister has ruled out a
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry into the Southern Trust
OL,8,Fcervical smear scandal.
OL,10,FIt comes after an expert review which
OL,11,Fwas announced by Mike Nesbitt in
OL,12,FNovember 2025, following the
OL,13,Fpublication of three other reviews.
OL,15,FAround 17,500 women in the Southern
OL,16,FTrust area who were screened between
OL,17,F2008 and 2021 had to have their
OL,18,Fresults rechecked after concerns were
OL,19,Fraised in a report by the Royal
OL,20,FCollege of Pathologists.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,FThe expert review was carried out by
OL,7,Fthe former chief medical officer for
OL,8,FWales, Professor Sir Frank Atherton.
OL,10,FIt aimed to look at the apparent
OL,11,Ffailures in the Northern Ireland
OL,12,FCervical Screening Programme (NICSP)
OL,13,Fand to outline what should be done to
OL,14,Fensure the future safety and
OL,15,Feffectiveness of the service.
OL,17,FThe expert review also considered a
OL,18,Fnumber of women and families who were
OL,19,Faffected by theJprogramme and the
OL,20,Fcampaign group 'Ladies with Letters'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,FSir Frank said he heard the "anxieties
OL,7,F(largely from officials) that a public
OL,8,Finquiry would be time consuming, risk
OL,9,Fre-traumatisation, further delay
OL,10,Fresolution, involve significant
OL,11,Fexpense, and potentially fail to
OL,12,Fdeliver any greater clarity on the
OL,13,Fnature and extent of programme
OL,14,Ffailures which are documented in the
OL,15,Fcommissioned reports and summarised
OL,16,Fhere."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,F"I believe that it is highly unlikely
OL,7,Fthat a statutory inquiry would be able
OL,8,Fto make further progress on
OL,9,Funravelling the technical aspects of
OL,10,Fthe programme failure which I have
OL,11,Fsummarised," he added.
OL,13,F"With regard to the role of a
OL,14,Fstatutory inquiry in assigning
OL,15,Faccountability, it should be clear
OL,16,Ffrom this
OL,18,Fsummary report that there have been
OL,19,Fsignificant failures in management and
OL,20,Fgovernance by the
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,Forganisations which were responsible
OL,7,Ffor delivery and oversight of the
OL,8,Fcervical screening programme."
OL,10,FThe Health Minister said he recognised
OL,11,Fthe "particularly difficult and
OL,12,Fchallenging time for the women and
OL,13,Ftheir families who have been impacted
OL,14,Fby cervical cancer."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,FMike Nesbitt said: "Sir Frank
OL,7,Fconcluded that while there have been
OL,8,Fsignificant failings, a statutory
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry is highly unlikely to
OL,10,Fprovide any further clarity. I accept
OL,11,Fthese findings and advice from Sir
OL,12,FFrank.
OL,14,F"A Statutory Public Inquiry is a means
OL,15,Fto an end, that end being answering
OL,16,Fkey questions. I believe those answers
OL,17,Fhave been addressed as far as that is
OL,18,Fpossible. We know what happened, why
OL,19,Fit happened, who was responsible and
OL,20,Fwhat has been done to try to ensure it
OL,21,Fnever happens again."
OL,26,@nD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
