PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779109902
OL,3,CNo public inquiry into cervical smear
OL,4,Cscandal
OL,6,F"I recognise that this decision will
OL,7,Fbe disappointing for many. I want to
OL,8,Freassure them that lessons have been
OL,9,Flearnt and we will continue to make
OL,10,Fdevelopments to improve our Cervical
OL,11,FScreening Programme in Northern
OL,12,FIreland."
